          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099099/Van Dale groot woordenboek (1994)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Xictequihui para ticmanextiz ce ixxayactli tlen motlalia ipan toixco huan quence quitzacua nochi toixco. Nochipa timotlalhuilia quence para ma techpalehui zo quemman oncah ce mihtotiliztli tlen ce campeca africana huan tlen cequinoc tlaneltoquilli.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
